text: Arda Kızıldağ (born 15 October 1998) is a Turkish professional footballer who plays as a defender for Gençlerbirliği in the Turkish Süper Lig. ==Professional career== Kızıldağ made his professional debut for Gençlerbirliği in a 4-0 Süper Lig loss to Gazişehir Gaziantep F.K. on 26 August 2019. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:People from Yenimahalle Category:Turkish footballers Category:Gençlerbirliği S.K. footballers Category:Hacettepe S.K. footballers Category:Süper Lig players Category:TFF First League players Category:Association football defenders
